title: Become homeowner today with only $10,000 down ! I will help you!
posting_body: ['The CALHFA MYHOME Down Payment Assistance Program allows a 1st Time Home Buyer to', 'purchase any Home for only $10,000 down!!!', 'Why continue paying rent making your landlord rich when you can OWN YOUR OWN HOME', 'TODAY!!!!', 'Stop making your landlord rich!', 'RENT will only keep increasing year after year!', 'Renting has NO', 'TAX BENEFITS.', 'When you Own A HOME your payment NEVER goes up.. instead, it goes down over time.', 'AND', 'YOU RECEIVE MAJOR $$$ TAX BENEFITS!', 'You also build $$$ EQUITY over time, our past clients have earned $50,000 to $200,000 in', 'equity in as little as 2 years. . .', 'could you save $200,000 in 2 years while renting?', "Even if your rent is only $1,500 a month that's $90,000 in 5 years..and $180,000 in 10 years..", 'that money could be going towards paying down your OWN home and into YOUR pocket', "instead of your Landlord's pocket.", 'If you OWNED for 10 years, you would never have a payment increase, & YOU WOULD HAVE', 'PAID OFF MORE THAN HALF OF YOUR OWN HOME AND BUILT MAJOR $$$ EQUITY!', 'CALL US TODAY TO EXPLORE YOUR OPTIONS!', 'EASY TO QUALIFY!', 'BAD CREDIT OK!', 'BANKRUPTCY IS OK!', 'FORECLOSURE IS OK!', 'SHORT SALE OK.', 'Tony Ayoub', 'Berkshire Hathaway Home Services', '9917 Walker Street, Cypress CA 90630', 'BRE 01717910', 'Direct', 'show contact info', '<URL>', 'Down payment based on CALHFA MyHOME Down Payment assistance program approval,', 'Payments based on 360 total payments, APR 6.750% or the best prevailing rate at the time of lock,', 'O.A.C., MCC Tax Credit, subject to change without notice.']
